\define my_editor(field)
<$edit-text field="$field$" tag="textarea" class="tc-edit-texteditor"/>
\end

<$appear show="field editor">
<$macrocall $name="my_editor"  field={{_my/ui/EditTemplate/field_editor/state}} />
</$appear>

<$select tiddler='_my/ui/EditTemplate/field_editor/state'>
<$list filter="[<currentTiddler>fields[]prefix[.]]">
<option value=<<currentTiddler>> ><<currentTiddler>></option>
<$/list>
</$select>
